Warszawa Wola Grzybowska railway station is a railway station in the Wesoła district of Warsaw, Poland. As of 2012, it is served by Koleje Mazowieckie, who run the KM2 services from Warszawa Zachodnia to Łuków and by Szybka Kolej Miejska, who run the S2 services from Warszawa Zachodnia to Sulejówek Miłosna.
